Summary of Required Tools
Tool	Version Required	Description
Node.js	12.x or higher	JavaScript runtime to run the backend
npm	Latest (comes with Node.js)	Dependency management and script running
MongoDB	4.x or higher	Database for storing user data and chat messages
React	18.x or higher	Frontend framework for building the user interface
Express	Latest	Framework for building the Node.js backend
Socket.io	Latest	Real-time communication (WebSockets)
Axios	Latest	Promise-based HTTP client for making API requests
bcryptjs	Latest	Password hashing library
jsonwebtoken	Latest	JSON Web Token implementation for authentication
dotenv	Latest	For managing environment variables
cors	Latest	Cross-origin resource sharing package for allowing frontend-backend communication
